snippet.title: The Bitmap Brothers Collection 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Evercade VS. While the first collection only had console versions, all but one game on the second cart are Amiga titles. Therefore, the cart is considered as a home computer cart. Remember: console carts are in red boxes, while computer carts come in blue.

Games in this cart:
00:00 - Intro
00:20 - Cadaver
10:31 - Cadaver: The Payoff
19:35 - Gods
30:00 - Magic Pockets
41:12 - The Chaos Engine 2
48:00 - Z (PSone Ver.)

The Bitmap Brothers, Cadaver, Cadaver: The Payoff, Gods, Magic Pockets, The Chaos Engine, The Chaos Engine 2, Z: The Game (C) Rebellion
